+# Word Garden
+
+A friendly terminal word-guessing game. Guess the hidden word before the garden runs out of water. It is like Hangman, but with plants instead of gallows.
+
+Word Garden is a small TUI game designed as a more cheerful alternative to Hangman. It is intended as a slightly more adventurous "Hello World" project for testing AI-assisted software development. The game includes input validation, state management, a simple loop, win/loss conditions, and a friendly terminal interface.
+
+## How to Play
+
+Start the game:
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden
+```
+
+The game will display a masked word and prompt you for a letter guess. Each correct guess reveals matching letters and helps your garden grow. Each incorrect guess costs water and allows weeds to spread.
+
+Win by revealing all the letters before the garden runs out of water.
+
+## Options
+
+**Difficulty levels:**
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty easy      # 8 water, 4–6 letter words
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty normal    # 6 water, 5–8 letter words (default)
+python3 -m word_garden --difficulty hard      # 4 water, 7+ letter words
+```
+
+**ASCII mode (no emoji):**
+
+```bash
+python3 -m word_garden --ascii
+```
+
+## Rules
+
+- The game picks a random secret word.
+- You guess one letter at a time.
+- A correct guess reveals all matching positions and helps your plant grow.
+- An incorrect guess costs one water and adds a weed.
+- You win by revealing the entire word.
+- You lose if the garden runs out of water before the word is complete.
+
+## Example Game
+
+```
+🌱 Word Garden
+
+Word:     _ _ _ _ _ _
+Guessed:
+Water:   💧💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:
+
+Guess a letter: a
+
+Good guess! The garden grows.
+
+Word:     _ A _ _ _ _
+Guessed:  A
+Water:   💧💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:
+
+Guess a letter: z
+
+No match. A weed appears.
+
+Word:     _ A _ _ _ _
+Guessed:  A Z
+Water:   💧💧💧💧💧
+Weeds:   🌿
+```
+
+## Accessibility
+
+The game supports both emoji and ASCII modes. In ASCII mode, water and weeds are shown as counts with text labels, so the game is fully playable without emoji support.
+
+```
+Water: 5/6 [*****]
+Weeds: 1 [-]
+```
